{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"10bd2471dd","title":"关于调查山西省和顺、昔阳两县农民缺粮情况的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"20fde7c307","index":0,"year":1955,"month":7,"day":8,"articleId":"10bd2471dd"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/35-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji35":{"comments":[{"id":"400bf89e13","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"10bd2471dd","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"《人民日报》总编室1955年7月6日编印的《人民日报情况》登载的《读者反映山西和顺、普阳两县农民缺粮情况严重》的材料说：据6月中句收到的读者来信反映，山西省和顺、普阳两县农民缺粮情况十分严重，不少农民放弃了生产，成群结队到外地投亲或行艺，有的地方已出现卖子女、离婚等现象。由于粮食问题得不到解决，农民忽言很多，反动地主、富农和暗藏的反革命分子也整机活动，各种谣言不断出现。读者在来信中要求党和政府迅速派人下去查明情况，解决农民的缺粮问题。"}],"contents":[{"id":"03e159dd06","type":"title","text":"关于调查山西省和顺、普阳两县农民缺粮情况的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"10bd2471dd"},{"id":"400bf89e13","type":"paragraph","text":"小平同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"10bd2471dd"},{"id":"6e9b06b970","type":"paragraph","text":"此件第五页所载山西两个县缺粮情况问是否属实，请转山西省委派人前往调查，以其结果报告中央为盼","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"10bd2471dd"},{"id":"892f6c69e7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"10bd2471dd"},{"id":"d6db5c9bc3","type":"paragraph","text":"七月八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"10bd2471dd"},{"id":"ce6b983ef8","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]小平，即邓小平，当时任中共中央秘书长、国务院副总理。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"10bd2471dd"}],"page":{"id":"7defa335c4","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"10bd2471dd","start":188,"end":188}}}},"__N_SSG":true}